%N A396023 Decimal expansion of (Pi+2)/Pi^2.
%C A396023 The probability that Buffon's needle (see A060294), bent at its midpoint at a uniformly random angle between 0 and 360 degrees, will land on a line when dropped onto a floor with parallel lines spaced at a distance equal to the length of the needle.
%H A396023 Uwe Bäsel, <a href="https://doi.org/10.5169/seals-630622">Buffon's problem with a pivot needle</a>, Elemente der Mathematik, Vol. 70, No. 2 (2015), pp. 67-70. See Remark 1, p. 70.
